title: #92Noon! Vox In The Box/Pierre McGuire/Eric Kendricks/Boudreau/Russo/Rachel Ramsey/Tennabee
description: Paul Allen and Nordo are live from the Xcel for the Wild's practice and Vox in the Box. They are joined by NBC's Pierre McGuire, Minnesota Viking Eric Kendricks, the FAN's Brandon Tennabee Mileski, head coach, Bruce Boudreau, The Athletic's Mike Russo, and Pronger with a pony-tail Rachel Ramsey!
